"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.13.3.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.13.3.2</span> 标题：要塞、堡垒、城堡（fortress, stronghold, castle, citadel, fort）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בִּירָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：birah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:12\">2CH 17:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr27:4\">2CH 27:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:8\">NEH 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:2\">NEH 7:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִבְצָר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mivtsar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:7\">2SA 24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:12\">2KI 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:41\">PSA 89:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:3\">ISA 17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:13\">ISA 34:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:18\">JER 48:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:2\">LAM 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:5\">LAM 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:39\">DAN 11:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:14\">HOS 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:9\">AMO 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:10\">MIC 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:12\">NAM 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:14\">NAM 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:10\">HAB 1:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִגְדַּל־שְׁכֶם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：migdal shkem)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:46\">JDG 9:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:47\">JDG 9:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:49\">JDG 9:49</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִסְגֶּרֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：misgereth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:46\">2SA 22:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:46\">PSA 18:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:17\">MIC 7:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מָעוֹז</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：ma‘oz)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:11\">ISA 23:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:7\">DAN 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:10\">DAN 11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:10\">DAN 11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:19\">DAN 11:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:31\">DAN 11:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:38\">DAN 11:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:39\">DAN 11:39</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מְצָד, מְצוּדָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mtsad, mtsudah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:7\">2SA 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:9\">2SA 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:5\">1CH 11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:7\">1CH 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:41\">JER 48:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:30\">JER 51:30</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מָצוֹר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：matsor)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:3\">ZEC 9:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מְצוּרָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mtsurah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr11:11\">2CH 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr11:23\">2CH 11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:4\">2CH 12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:5\">2CH 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:3\">2CH 21:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִשְׂגָּב</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：misgav)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:3\">2SA 22:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:10\">PSA 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:10\">PSA 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:3\">PSA 18:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:8\">PSA 46:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:12\">PSA 46:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:4\">PSA 48:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:10\">PSA 59:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:17\">PSA 59:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:18\">PSA 59:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:3\">PSA 62:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:7\">PSA 62:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:22\">PSA 94:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:2\">PSA 144:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:12\">ISA 25:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:16\">ISA 33:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:1\">JER 48:1</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：צְרִיחַ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tsariach)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:46\">JDG 9:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:49\">JDG 9:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:49\">JDG 9:49</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἀκρόπολις</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：akropolis)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc4:12\">2MA 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc4:28\">2MA 4:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc5:5\">2MA 5:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἄκρα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：akra)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:33\">1MA 1:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc3:45\">1MA 3:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc4:2\">1MA 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc4:41\">1MA 4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:18\">1MA 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:26\">1MA 6:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:32\">1MA 6:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc9:52\">1MA 9:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc9:53\">1MA 9:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:7\">1MA 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:7\">1MA 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:9\">1MA 10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:32\">1MA 10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:21\">1MA 11:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:21\">1MA 11:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:41\">1MA 11:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc12:36\">1MA 12:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:21\">1MA 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:50\">1MA 13:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:50\">1MA 13:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:52\">1MA 13:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc14:7\">1MA 14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc14:36\">1MA 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc15:28\">1MA 15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc15:31\">2MA 15:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc15:35\">2MA 15:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc4:20\">4MA 4:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：βάρις</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：baris)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd6:22\">1ES 6:22</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ὀχύρωμα, ὀχυρωμάτιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：ochurōma, ochurōmation)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:4\">2CO 10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:2\">1MA 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc4:61\">1MA 4:61</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:9\">1MA 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:11\">1MA 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:27\">1MA 5:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:29\">1MA 5:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:30\">1MA 5:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:65\">1MA 5:65</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:61\">1MA 6:61</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:62\">1MA 6:62</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc8:10\">1MA 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc9:50\">1MA 9:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:12\">1MA 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc10:37\">1MA 10:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:18\">1MA 11:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:18\">1MA 11:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc11:41\">1MA 11:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc12:33\">1MA 12:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc12:34\">1MA 12:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc12:35\">1MA 12:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc12:45\">1MA 12:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:33\">1MA 13:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:33\">1MA 13:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:38\">1MA 13:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc14:42\">1MA 14:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc15:7\">1MA 15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc16:8\">1MA 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc16:15\">1MA 16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc8:30\">2MA 8:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:15\">2MA 10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:16\">2MA 10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:23\">2MA 10:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:32\">2MA 10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc11:6\">2MA 11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc12:19\">2MA 12:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc6:25\">3MA 6:25</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：φρούριον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：frourion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:32\">2MA 10:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:33\">2MA 10:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc13:19\">2MA 13:19</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/PTZ-0066_antonia_fortress_model.jpg\" alt=\"耶路撒冷安东尼亚堡垒（Antonia Fortress）模型\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">耶路撒冷安东尼亚堡垒（Antonia Fortress）模型 (© Ray Pritz by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>堡垒是一种大型防御工事，通常是城镇防御的一部分。在中东，这种防御工事是用石头建造的。堡垒可能是一座特别坚固的建筑物，或者是一个建筑群，周围有自身的防护墙。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在有些语言中，“堡垒”一词可以根据其功能来翻译，例如译为“提供保护的地方”或“防卫自己的地方”。然而，堡垒通常是根据它的建筑结构来描述的，例如“有坚固围墙的地方”。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:8\">NEH 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:2\">NEH 7:2</a> 中，希伯来文<em>birah</em> 指的是位于耶路撒冷圣殿建筑群西北角的一处防御工事，用来防守圣殿北侧，那是敌人最有可能进攻的地方。后来，大希律扩大并加强了该防御工事，并把它命名为安东尼亚堡（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.20.1 铺道、石板地、铺石地、铺华石处 (pavement, The Pavement)&lt;REALIA:3.20.1&gt;</a> ）。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:8\">NEH 2:8</a> 中，原文字面意思为“圣殿的堡垒”的短语可译为“靠近圣殿的堡垒”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 直译）、“防守圣殿的堡垒”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直译）、“紧挨着圣殿的要塞”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 直译）。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:47\">JDG 9:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:47\">JDG 9:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:49\">JDG 9:49</a> 中，不同译本对希伯来文短语<em>migdal shkem</em> 有不同的理解。我们查阅的大部分译本都将其译为“示剑塔”或“示剑城堡”；有些译本将“Tower”（“城楼、塔”）的首字母大写，表明它可能是一个地名。许多非英文译本（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Spanish Common Language Version (Dios Habla Hoy)\">SPCL</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"French Common Language Version (Bible en français courant)\">FRCL</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Dutch Common Language Version\">DUCL</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Traduction Oecuménique de la Bible (French, 1975)\">TOB</abbr> ）把它当做地名，仅仅进行了音译（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Dutch Common Language Version\">DUCL</abbr> 译为“米格达尔—示剑”）。</p>\n<p>在新约中，希腊文<em>ochurōma</em> 仅出现在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:4\">2CO 10:4</a> ，喻指谬论的力量。许多语言可能更适合采用明喻来翻译该词，以突出原文中的比喻用法；例如，这节经文可译为：“我们争战所用的兵器不是这世界的兵器，而是上帝大能的兵器，我们用这兵器可以摧毁谬论，就像人们摧毁堡垒一样。”</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
